.TH "xxxfb_copyarea" 9 "xxxfb_copyarea" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
xxxfb_copyarea \- REQUIRED function. Can use generic routines if non acclerated hardware and packed pixel based. Copies one area of the screen to another area.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" xxxfb_copyarea
.BI "(struct fb_info *p "  ","
.BI "const struct fb_copyarea *area "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "p" 12
-- undescribed --
.IP "area" 12
Structure providing the data to copy the framebuffer contents
from one region to another.

This drawing operation copies a rectangular area from one area of the
screen to another area.
